description: The OtterBox Defender Series iPod touch 5G case is made for adventure. Whether that's braving urban traffic on a bicycle or bouncing around in a backpack full of textbooks, this case is made to live through the worst with your iPod touch safely inside. Go with confidence and never worry about where and when it is safe to use. The Defender Series iPod touch 5G case is practically indestructible.
title: OtterBox Defender Series Case for iPod touch 5G - Boom
